{
  "1854570": {
    "name": "巨像要塞",
    "steam_appid": 1854570,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/f3659dfde571e6584dd850ae0464d235.avif?t=1753777654\" width=616 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《巨像要塞》是一款硬核类肉鸽策略游戏，您将在无垠之海的未知大陆上扩张属于自己的领地，  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个人都是生产与战争中至关重要的一环。谁都能成为英雄，为最终的胜利贡献自己的力量。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着时间推移，向着从未有人踏足的土地扩张。在探索新资源（从稀有矿物到龙类族群）与采集已发掘资源之间维持住脆弱的平衡。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/332dbc462fcd32b94ca52b734e7a64bd.avif?t=1753777654\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/9de43c06384cad45dbf3e5085399d39a.poster.avif?t=1753777654\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/9de43c06384cad45dbf3e5085399d39a.webm?t=1753777654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/9de43c06384cad45dbf3e5085399d39a.mp4?t=1753777654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有的角色都是独一无二的。他们有自己的属性、技能和背景故事，还会随着时间逐渐变化。你可以促进他们朝特定方向成长，但他们也会自主战斗并强化。任何人都可以成为英雄：即便是最常见的农民、木匠或铁匠，也能在技艺登峰造极后打造出杰作，为你带来经济上的优势。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/27508f114565224e3f2747e7b58c57d7.avif?t=1753777654\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/8a9ef7510058c09bb95031b9991c8659.poster.avif?t=1753777654\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/8a9ef7510058c09bb95031b9991c8659.webm?t=1753777654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/8a9ef7510058c09bb95031b9991c8659.mp4?t=1753777654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩张领地，将新资源纳入管辖，将它们组合起来发挥出更加强大的力量。你的每一次选择都将影响势力的实力与形象。知己知彼，方能百战不殆。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/2a8bc61caf0d39eb4faf26b984435f0e.avif?t=1753777654\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/fb59172084de3d20333e731fd01ca7f0.poster.avif?t=1753777654\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/fb59172084de3d20333e731fd01ca7f0.webm?t=1753777654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/fb59172084de3d20333e731fd01ca7f0.mp4?t=1753777654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城镇建设与战斗将在大地图上同时进行。极简的控制界面与众多自动化功能，可以最大限度地减少微操管理。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在具有地形和时间机制的回合制战斗中，充分发挥你的战略技巧。你可以控制数十名不同等级的战士，也可以扮演“独狼”。在地图上进行建设的同时，无缝展开回合制战斗，通过分析与预测获得最终的胜利。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/a475915aa887f815ceec233ce59ff5d5.avif?t=1753777654\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帝国终有落幕之时，但你可以从失败中学习，然后重新开始！不过，每一轮你都将探索一个完全不同的世界，那里有程序生成的独特景观、文明和自然资源。你必须不断尝试和调整策略，才能完成任务目标（或者其他的隐藏任务）。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854570/extras/c4d62e175f7a671cf7f281f8ed7774d2.avif?t=1753777654\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在肉鸽模式中与好友组队，也可以在竞技模式中与好友展开对决！双方回合同时进行，可以取消，并且对反应速度没有任何要求：只需要利用游戏的预测机制精心规划行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>筑起要塞，发展经济，培养英雄！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
